description: Party Time can tell you if a given date is a Holiday, what holiday is coming up next, or what the last holiday was. The current version only supports US holidays, but the underlying API supports many countries - Support for those is coming soon.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Party Time is today a holiday
name: Party Time
shortDescription: Party Time can tell you if a given date is a Holiday, what holiday is coming up next, or what the last holiday was.
